    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5557758/" class="title-link">这两年我看过最好的国内小说</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5557758"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/pinkpigbond/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u9984202-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pinkpigbond/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">粉红猪猪侠</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-08-23"
      class="main-meta">2012-08-23 14:34:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5557758_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  “顺从得令人发指”这句话是作家阿丁的QQ签名档，他说这句话是前苏联作家巴别尔在某次苏联作协会议上说的，当年他读到这句话的时候，就好像是挨了一拳，突然意识到周边的人，包括亲朋好友以及自己，都是一群“顺从得令人发指”的人，顺从似乎已经成了流淌在人们血液中的哲学。...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5557758/#comments">(18回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">40有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5557758_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5557758_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





